===You have a message. Receiving...===
{{Messages|text=
:{{DIcon|Warning}} You have a message. Receiving...
:'''Cyrene:''' Partner, by the time you receive this message, ripples should already have departed
:'''Cyrene:''' Before turning away, I took one last look at the stars. Look~
:'''Cyrene:''' [[File:Message Cyrene 50.png|256px]]
:'''Cyrene:''' Every time I look at the stars, I imagine what I could do in the cosmos
:'''Cyrene:''' Hehe, Cyrene, the Knight of Beauty. Sounds pretty great, don't you think?
:'''Cyrene:''' If I open my mind a little, wouldn't I make a good "Stella Hunter"? Or maybe... a Nameless?
:'''Cyrene:''' But those wishes are far too extravagant
:'''Cyrene:''' I already have a star that no one else has ever had, right♪
:'''Cyrene:''' As long as I gaze at it longingly, light will fall into my eyes
:'''Cyrene:''' Maybe this is my greatest wish...
:'''Cyrene:''' (Trailblazer), on the long road ahead, you must keep on shining, alright?
:'''Cyrene:''' Oh, did I make the atmosphere too sad...?
:'''Cyrene:''' Then just look up at the sky and smile!
:'''Cyrene:''' Wherever you go, the stars of Amphoreus will forever twinkle for you, just like I am winking at you~
:'''Cyrene:''' And then, we will surely, surely meet again beneath the starlight ♪
:'''Cyrene:''' {{tx|Missing sticker}}{{subst:void|<!--SpriteOutput/Emoji/124009.png-->}}
:{Choice} We'll definitely meet again...
::'''(Trailblazer):''' We'll definitely meet again
:{Choice} When will we meet again?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' When will we meet again?
:{Choice} That's a promise. We will go stargazing together
::'''(Trailblazer):''' That's a promise. We will go stargazing together
