===You have a message. Receiving...===
{{Messages|text=
:{{DIcon|Warning}} You have a message. Receiving...
:'''Cyrene:''' Ta-da!
:'''Cyrene:''' A girl named Cyrene would never leave so easily~
:'''Cyrene:''' Another beautiful day. And of course, it needs flowers to make it complete ♪
:'''Cyrene:''' {{tx|Missing sticker}}{{subst:void|<!--SpriteOutput/Emoji/124012.png-->}}
:'''Cyrene:''' Ah, I really put a lot of thought into choosing this bouquet
:'''Cyrene:''' A prismatic crystal rose, grown from a single seed, carefully nurtured by my own hands~
:'''Cyrene:''' Hehe, and the Antila flowers from Castorice's garden, each petal shimmering with dewdrops
:'''Cyrene:''' Sunflowers and canterbury bells from Hyacine's courtyard, like gentle sunlight~
:'''Cyrene:''' And there are blue moonlight lilies, baby's breath, white bellflowers...
:'''Cyrene:''' Hehe, can you guess... what my favorite combination is?
:'''Cyrene:''' Ta-da! A bundle of wheat of Aedes Elysiae!
:'''Cyrene:''' (Trailblazer), when you receive it, remember to close your eyes. The scent of wheat will transport you right back to that little village
:'''Cyrene:''' Just like back then, when we swung high on the swings, waves crashed on the distant shore and wheat fields surged beneath our feet...
:'''Cyrene:''' The rest of the surprises are for you to discover!
:'''Cyrene:''' Even if I cannot be there with you, make sure to read the message on the card carefully, alright?
:'''Cyrene:''' May flowers accompany you every day, (Trailblazer)♪
:{Choice} Thank you, Cyrene
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Thank you, Cyrene
:{Choice} I have received your heartfelt gesture
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I have received your heartfelt gesture
:{Choice} I'll keep it safe!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'll keep it safe!
